      {
        title: 'Is AstroMvp compatible with the latest versions of React and Bootstrap?',
        description:
          'Yes, AstroMvp is designed to be compatible with the latest versions of both React and Bootstrap. This ensures that you can leverage the full power of these technologies while taking advantage of the features offered by AstroMvp.',
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
